data.description: Live up on St Joes ridge with million dollar views! Excellent location overlooking the valley with amazing sunsets. Priced at appraised value when sellers purchased. Easy commute to La Crosse, Onalaska or West Salem. Spacious living room welcomes you with 3BRs on the main and one in the lower level. Full bath on each level along with laundry on lower level. 2-car garage that leads to lower level family room. All mechanicals newer, low property taxes, come see this beauty today!
